WEBVTT

00:01.213 --> 00:03.460
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...

00:03.463 --> 00:05.124
Bet you didn't see that coming.

00:05.126 --> 00:07.160
Go... to hell.

00:07.162 --> 00:09.028
You first.

00:11.666 --> 00:13.866
SELINE: <i>When the door
between this world and Cade's</i>

00:13.868 --> 00:17.263
<i>gets cracked open, it wipes
out everything for miles.</i>

00:17.266 --> 00:18.204
<i>In this case...</i>

00:18.206 --> 00:19.739
All of us in Mystic Falls.

00:19.741 --> 00:21.255
<i>All you got to do is make sure</i>

00:21.258 --> 00:22.709
<i>that bell rings 12 times.</i>

00:22.711 --> 00:25.378
I thought you had to figure things out.

00:25.380 --> 00:28.281
I couldn't see that everything
that I was looking for

00:28.283 --> 00:30.116
was right here in you.

00:30.118 --> 00:31.351
Will you marry me?

00:31.353 --> 00:32.719
Yes, of course.

00:33.955 --> 00:35.021
You didn't destroy hell.

00:35.023 --> 00:36.189
Thanks to you killing Cade,

00:36.191 --> 00:37.657
hell's never been in better hands.

00:37.659 --> 00:40.093
If Cade's not running hell, who is?

00:40.095 --> 00:42.362
The person who knows where
all your weak spots are.

00:42.364 --> 00:44.030
The one who wants revenge

00:44.032 --> 00:46.032
for what we did to her.

00:46.034 --> 00:47.700
Don't you dare say that name!

00:47.702 --> 00:49.502
The baddest bitch of all.

00:49.504 --> 00:51.838
Katherine.

00:57.732 --> 00:59.732
_

