40:50.274 --> 40:52.941
♪ ♪

41:03.754 --> 41:05.453
[bell tolls]

41:08.425 --> 41:10.125
There's Vicki.

41:10.127 --> 41:12.093
Right on time.

41:15.966 --> 41:17.799
[gags, coughs]

41:17.801 --> 41:19.885
[gasps]

41:19.887 --> 41:21.887
♪ Whoa, oh, oh ♪

41:21.889 --> 41:24.139
♪ Oh, oh... ♪

41:24.141 --> 41:25.223
[groans]

41:25.809 --> 41:27.142
Mom...

41:30.447 --> 41:34.032
♪ Darlin', I don't know
what you've done to me ♪

41:34.034 --> 41:39.154
